snippet.title: Rocket League Season 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Rocket League Season 2 drops December 9, 2020! For more details visit: https://www.rocketleague.com/seasons/season-2/

🔊It's time to get loud!🔊 The latest season of Rocket League will celebrate all things music with a new Rocket Pass, Arena, Competitive Season, a new customization option called Player Anthems, new content from hit artist Kaskade, and much more!

Download and play Rocket League for free on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and Epic Games Store.

Epic Games Store : https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/rocket-league/home 

Listen to "Flip Reset" By Kaskade and WILL K available now: https://monstercat.ffm.to/flipreset-xxmj

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSeason2
